'''馬爾谷·韋萊'''，{{link-en|聖蘇比許司鐸會|Society of the Priests of Saint Sulpice|P.S.S.}}（{{lang-en|Marc Ouellet}}；{{bd|1944年|6月8日|catIdx=Marc Ouellet}}）是[[加拿大人|加拿大籍]][[天主教|天主教]][[樞機|樞機]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Hopper |first1=Tristin |title=Canadian Cardinal Marc Ouellet reportedly helped broker resignation of scandal-plagued U.K. cardinal |url=https://nationalpost.com/news/canadian-cardinal-marc-ouellet-reportedly-helped-broker-resignation-of-scandal-plagued-u-k-cardinal |accessdate=2018-12-24 |publisher=National Post |date=2013-03-01 |archivedate=2018-12-26 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>、聖蘇比許司鐸會會士、現任[[聖座|聖座]]{{link-en|主教部|Congregation for Bishops|主教部部長}}和{{link-en|宗座拉丁美洲委員會|Pontifical Commission for Latin America|宗座拉丁美洲委員會主席}}。從2002年到2010年期間，他曾擔任[[天主教魁北克總教區|魁北克總教區總主教]]和加拿大[[首席主教|首席主教]]。[[教宗若望保祿二世|教宗若望保祿二世]]於2003年將他擢升為樞機。[[教宗本篤十六世|教宗本篤十六世]]於2013年退位後，他被視為其中一個有較大機會接任[[教宗|教宗]]的人選<ref>{{cite news |last1=Thompson |first1=Nick |title=Gambling with God: Staking a wager on the next pope |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2013/02/28/world/europe/vatican-pope-odds/index.html |accessdate=2018-12-24 |publisher=CNN |date=2013-03-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224130634/https://edition.cnn.com/2013/02/28/world/europe/vatican-pope-odds/index.html |archivedate=2018-12-24 |language=en}}</ref>。他能說[[法語|法語]]、[[英語|英語]]、[[德語|德語]]、[[意大利語|意大利語]]、[[葡萄牙語|葡萄牙語]]和[[西班牙語|西班牙語]]。<ref name="huff">{{cite news |last1=Fenlon |first1=Brodie |title=About Marc Ouellet: 13 Things You Didn't Know About The Canadian Cardinal |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2013/03/11/about-marc-ouellet-13-things-canadian-cardinal_n_2852462.html |accessdate=2018-12-24 |publisher=HuffPost |date=2013-03-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224152536/https://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2013/03/11/about-marc-ouellet-13-things-canadian-cardinal_n_2852462.html |archivedate=2018-12-24 |language=en}}</ref>

== 早年生活及司鐸時期 ==
韋萊於1944年6月8日在一個位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[魁北克省|魁北克省]]{{link-en|拉莫特 (魁北克省)|La Motte, Quebec|拉莫特}}的家庭出生。他在家中8名兄弟姐妹中排行第三，父親皮埃爾·韋萊（{{lang|en|Pierre Ouellet}}）是一名校長。他在17歲的時候曾因打[[曲棍球|曲棍球]]而令他的腿受傷；在這時，他閲讀了[[聖女小德蘭|聖女小德蘭]]的故事而開始思考故事的深層意義。1964年，他在[[拉瓦爾大學|拉瓦爾大學]]獲得{{link-en|教育學士|Bachelor of Education}}學位。從1964年開始，他進入修院修讀神學至1968年為止。同年，[[蒙特利尔大學|蒙特利尔大學]]向他頒發{{link-en|神學碩士|Licentiate of Theology}}學位。同年5月25日，他在[[天主教埃默斯教區|埃默斯教區]][[晉鐸|晉鐸]]並在{{link-en|金谷市 (魁北克省)|Val-d'Or|金谷市}}的{{link-en|聖索沃爾 (魁北克省)|Saint-Sauveur, Quebec|聖索沃爾}}堂區擔任[[助理牧師|助理主任司鐸]]一職。1970年，他卸下助理主任司鐸的職務並在同年末轉到[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]的{{link-en|波哥大大修院|Major Seminary of Bogotá}}教授哲學。他在1972年加入{{link-en|聖蘇比許司鐸會|Society of the Priests of Saint Sulpice}}。兩年後，他在{{link-en|宗座聖多瑪斯·亞奎那大學|Pontifical University of Saint Thomas Aquinas}}獲得[[執業學位|哲學碩士]]並在1983年在[[宗座額我略大學|宗座額我略大學]]獲得{{link-en|信理神學|Dogmatic theology}}博士學位。他曾任3所修道院的院長，亦曾是{{link-en|聖職部|Congregation for the Clergy}}和聖蘇比許司鐸會總部議會的{{link-en|參議員 (天主教)|Consultor|參議員}}。1996年，他成為{{link-en|宗座拉特朗大學|Pontifical Lateran University}}{{link-en|若望保祿二世宗座婚姻及家庭科學神學院|John Paul II Pontifical Theological Institute for Marriage and Family Sciences|若望保祿二世婚姻及家庭研究院}}信理神學教授。<ref name="Salvador" /><ref name="huff" /><ref name="SPSS">{{cite web |title=Biography of Cardinal Marc Ouellet, p.s.s. |url=http://www.sulpc.org/evsulpc_ouellet_en.php |publisher=Province of Canada, Society of the Priests of Saint Sulpice |accessdate=2018-12-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224154515/http://www.sulpc.org/evsulpc_ouellet_en.php |archivedate=2018-12-24 |language=en}}</ref><ref name="ECDQ">{{cite web |title=Marc Ouellet |url=https://www.ecdq.org/diocese-de-quebec/eveques/marc-ouellet/ |publisher=Église Catholique de Québec |accessdate=2018-12-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225052912/https://www.ecdq.org/diocese-de-quebec/eveques/marc-ouellet/ |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=fr}}</ref>

== 主教及總主教時期 ==
韋萊於2001年3月3日獲委任為[[宗座基督徒合一促進理事會|宗座基督徒合一促進理事會]]秘書長及[[阿格羅波利|阿格羅波利]]{{link-en|領銜教區|Titular See}}[[領銜主教|領銜主教]]。16日後，[[教宗若望·保祿二世|教宗若望·保祿二世]]於[[聖伯多祿大殿|聖伯多祿大殿]]將他[[祝聖|祝聖]]為主教。這場晉牧禮由教宗主禮，時任[[國務院_(聖座)|聖座國務卿]][[安傑洛·索達諾|安傑洛·索達諾]]和{{link-en|主教部部長|Congregation for Bishops}}[[若翰·雷|若翰·雷]]兩位[[樞機|樞機]]襄禮。<ref name="SPSS" /><ref name="VaticanPO">{{cite web |title=OUELLET Card. Marc, P.S.S. |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_ouellet_m.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2018-12-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225074823/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_ouellet_m.html |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en}}</ref>韋萊於同年6月12日獲委任為[[信理部|信理部]]的{{link-en|參議員 (天主教)|Consultor|參議員}}。<ref>{{cite news |title=Canadian Appointed to Doctrine of the Faith |url=https://zenit.org/articles/canadian-appointed-to-doctrine-of-the-faith/ |accessdate=2018-12-25 |publisher=Zenit News Agency |date=2001-06-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225082035/https://zenit.org/articles/canadian-appointed-to-doctrine-of-the-faith/ |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en}}</ref>翌年11月15日，他獲任命為[[天主教魁北克總教區|魁北克總教區總主教]]，接替退休的{{link-en|瑪利斯·庫特尤厄|Maurice Couture}}。他於2003年1月26日就職，若望保祿二世於6月29日在聖伯多祿大殿向他授予[[披帶|披帶]]。<ref name="Salvador" /><ref>{{cite news |title=Cardinal Ouellet to Head Bishops' Congregation |url=https://zenit.org/articles/cardinal-ouellet-to-head-bishops-congregation/ |accessdate=2018-12-25 |publisher=Zenit News Agency |date=2010-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225081234/https://zenit.org/articles/cardinal-ouellet-to-head-bishops-congregation/ |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 15.11.2002 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2002/11/15/0565/01787.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721072932/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2002/11/15/0565/01787.html |archivedate=2019-07-21 |language=it |date=2002-11-15}}</ref>

== 樞機時期 ==
[[File:KennyOullet&Johnson.jpg|thumb]]和[[賈森·康尼|賈森·康尼]]在{{link-en|教宗方濟各就職禮|Papal inauguration of Pope Francis}}舉行前一晚的合照]]
[[教宗若望保祿二世|教宗若望保祿二世]]於2003年10月21日的{{link-en|教宗樞密會議|Papal consistory|樞密會議}}上將韋萊擢升為司鐸級樞機，韋萊同時接替{{link-en|吉拉·艾米特·卡特|Gerald Emmett Carter}}而領{{link-en|過橋聖母堂|Santa Maria in Traspontina|過橋聖母堂區司鐸}}銜。<ref name="Salvador" /><ref>{{cite web |last1=Miranda |first1=Salvador |title=Ss. Marcellino e Pietro --- S. Matteo in Merulana |url=https://webdept.fiu.edu/~mirandas/titles-4.htm |publisher=Florida International University |accessdate=2018-12-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225092924/https://webdept.fiu.edu/~mirandas/titles-4.htm |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en}}</ref>韋萊有參與[[2005年教宗選舉秘密會議|2005年教宗選舉秘密會議]]，並被視作為其中一個有{{link-en|潛在教宗|Papabile|較大機會繼任教宗}}的人。該次選舉秘密會議最終選出[[本篤十六世|本篤十六世]]。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Glatz |first1=Carol |title=Life in Latin America, Quebec, Rome gives cardinal unique world view |url=http://www.catholicnews.com/services/englishnews/2013/life-in-latin-america-quebec-rome-gives-cardinal-unique-world-view.cfm |accessdate=2018-12-25 |publisher=Catholic News Service |date=2013-02-19 |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據{{link-en|小約翰·L·亞倫|John L. Allen Jr.}}同年在《{{link-en|國家天主教記者報|National Catholic Reporter}}》的報導，「曾與韋萊共事的人形容他是一個友善、謙遜、做事靈活和聰明的人」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Allen Jr. |first1=John L. |title=Who Will Be the Next Pope? |url=http://www.nationalcatholicreporter.org/update/conclave/top_candidates.htm |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=National Catholic Reporter |date=2005 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226140519/http://www.nationalcatholicreporter.org/update/conclave/top_candidates.htm |archivedate=2018-12-26 |language=en}}</ref>兩年後，他加入聖座組織與經濟問題研究樞機小組（{{lang|it|Consiglio di Cardinali per lo studio dei problemi organizzativi ed economici della Santa Sede}}）。<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 03.02.2007 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2007/02/03/0060/00160.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721073025/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2007/02/03/0060/00160.html |archivedate=2019-07-21 |language=it |date=2007-02-03}}</ref>2008年，身為[[天主教魁北克總教區|魁北克總教區總主教]]的他在該總教區主持了第49屆[[聖體大會|聖體大會]]。<ref>{{cite news |title=Eucharistic Congress opens with reflection on 'treasure of the Church' |url=https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/eucharistic-congress-opens-with-reflection-on-treasure-of-the-church |accessdate=2018-12-25 |publisher=Catholic News Agency |date=2012-06-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225120213/https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/eucharistic-congress-opens-with-reflection-on-treasure-of-the-church |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en}}</ref>同年10月，他擔任[[世界主教會議|世界主教會議]]第12屆常務會議的總發言人。<ref name="VaticanPO" />

本篤十六世於2010年6月30日任命韋萊為{{link-en|主教部|Congregation for Bishops|主教部部長}}及{{link-en|宗座拉丁美洲委員會|Pontifical Commission for Latin America|宗座拉丁美洲委員會主席}}，接替退休的[[若翰·雷|若翰·雷]]樞機。{{NoteTag|[[吉拉·拉克魯瓦|吉拉·拉克魯瓦]]於2011年2月接替韋萊，成為魁北克總教區總主教。<ref>{{cite news |title=Bishop Lacroix to succeed Cardinal Ouellet in Quebec City |url=https://www.catholicregister.org/canada/bishop-lacroix-to-succeed-cardinal-ouellet-in-quebec-city |accessdate=2018-12-29 |publisher=The Catholic Register |date=2011-02-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110228195356/https://www.catholicregister.org/canada/bishop-lacroix-to-succeed-cardinal-ouellet-in-quebec-city |archivedate=2011-02-28 |language=en}}</ref>}}<ref>{{cite news |title=Cardinal Ouellet appointed as head of Congregation for Bishops |url=https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/cardinal-ouellet-appointed-as-head-of-congregation-for-bishops |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=Catholic News Agency |date=2010-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226061227/https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/cardinal-ouellet-appointed-as-head-of-congregation-for-bishops |archivedate=2018-12-26 |language=en}}</ref>2011年1月5日，他獲委任為{{link-en|宗座新福音推廣理事會|Pontifical Council for Promoting the New Evangelization}}的首批成員。<ref>{{cite news |title=Archbishop Longley among members of new evangelisation council |url=https://catholicherald.co.uk/news/2011/01/05/archbishop-longley-among-members-of-new-evangelisation-council/ |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=Catholic Herald |date=2011-01-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226060559/https://catholicherald.co.uk/news/2011/01/05/archbishop-longley-among-members-of-new-evangelisation-council/ |archivedate=2018-12-26 |language=en}}</ref>24日後，他成為[[國務院_(聖座)|聖座國務院（外交事務處）]]的成員。<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 29.01.2011 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/01/29/0061/00138.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721073107/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/01/29/0061/00138.html |archivedate=2019-07-21 |language=it |date=2011-01-29}}</ref>[[教宗|教宗]]於4月6日委任他為{{link-en|宗座法典條文解釋理事會|Pontifical Council for Legislative Texts}}成員。<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 06.04.2011 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/04/06/0199/00492.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721073159/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2011/04/06/0199/00492.html |archivedate=2019-07-21 |language=it |date=2011-04-06}}</ref>同年6月，他公開談及在將來當選教宗的可能性。他表示如果他當選教宗的話，那將會是「一場噩夢」。此外，他認為「沒人會願意做教宗」，並覺得「教宗的壓力和肩負的責任都大」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Martin |first1=Stéphanie |title=Devenir pape «serait un cauchemar», dit Marc Ouellet |url=http://www.lapresse.ca/le-soleil/dossiers/labeaume-a-rome/201106/29/01-4413760-devenir-pape-serait-un-cauchemar-dit-marc-ouellet.php |accessdate=2018-12-25 |publisher=Le Soleil |date=2011-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170713205006/http://www.lapresse.ca/le-soleil/dossiers/labeaume-a-rome/201106/29/01-4413760-devenir-pape-serait-un-cauchemar-dit-marc-ouellet.php |archivedate=2017-07-13 |location=Québec |language=fr}}</ref>他於翌年3月7日獲教宗委任為[[東方教會部|東方教會部]]的成員。<ref>{{cite press release|title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 07.03.2012 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/03/07/0138/00319.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721073245/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/03/07/0138/00319.html |archivedate=2019-07-21 |language=it |date=2012-03-07}}</ref>韋萊自2010年起在羅馬居住。身為主教部部長，他需要在每周就主教任命等事項跟教宗會面一次。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Zervino |first1=María Lía |title=Interview with Cardinal Ouellet |url=http://www.osservatoreromano.va/en/news/when-spirit-intervenes |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=L'Osservatore Romano |date=2018-05-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226063315/http://www.osservatoreromano.va/en/news/when-spirit-intervenes |archivedate=2018-12-26 |language=en}}</ref>

此外，他亦有參與[[2013年教宗選舉秘密會議|2013年教宗選舉秘密會議]]。《{{link-en|二十四小時太陽報|Il Sole 24 Ore}}》的報導指出韋萊和[[教宗方濟各|伯格里奧]]（即教宗方濟各）在首3輪投票中得票「非常接近」。<ref>{{cite news |title=Canada's Ouellet beat Pope Francis in first rounds of voting, asked backers to switch support behind winner |url=https://nationalpost.com/holy-post/canadas-ouellet-beat-pope-francis-in-first-rounds-of-voting-reports |publisher=National Post |date=2013-03-15 |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en |access-date=2018-12-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>有意大利媒體相信他為了讓選舉盡快完結而要求他的支持者不要支持他，令伯格里奧當選教宗；不過韋萊因為「已發誓要將選舉秘密會議期間發生的事保密」而不肯談論這個話題。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Paquin |first1=Mali Ilse |title=Marc Ouellet se réjouit de l'élection de François |url=https://www.lapresse.ca/international/dossiers/succession-de-benoit-xvi/201303/15/01-4631518-marc-ouellet-se-rejouit-de-lelection-de-francois.php |accessdate=2018-12-25 |publisher=La Presse |date=2013-03-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225150335/https://www.lapresse.ca/international/dossiers/succession-de-benoit-xvi/201303/15/01-4631518-marc-ouellet-se-rejouit-de-lelection-de-francois.php |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=fr}}</ref>同年12月中，教宗方濟各確認他可繼續擔任主教部部長。<ref>{{cite news |title=Pope appoints, confirms members of bishops' congregation |url=https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/pope-appoints-confirms-members-of-bishops-congregation |accessdate=2018-12-25 |publisher=Catholic News Agency |date=2013-12-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225171754/https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/pope-appoints-confirms-members-of-bishops-congregation |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en}}</ref>

他於2014年2月19日獲續任東方教會部成員5年。<ref>{{cite news |title=Pope names new members of Congregation for Eastern Churches |url=https://www.ncronline.org/news/vatican/pope-names-new-members-congregation-eastern-churches |accessdate=2018-12-25 |agency=Catholic News Service |via=National Catholic Reporter |date=2014-02-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225173500/https://www.ncronline.org/news/vatican/pope-names-new-members-congregation-eastern-churches |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en}}</ref>方濟各於3月末任命他為{{link-en|獻身生活及使徒團體部|Congregation for Institutes of Consecrated Life and Societies of Apostolic Life}}成員<ref>{{cite news |last1=Glatz |first1=Carol |title=Pope Francis confirms heads of Vatican curial agencies |url=https://www.catholicregister.org/home/item/17866-pope-francis-confirms-heads-of-vatican-curial-agencies |accessdate=2018-12-26 |agency=Catholic News Service |via=The Catholic Register |date=2014-03-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226062237/https://www.catholicregister.org/home/item/17866-pope-francis-confirms-heads-of-vatican-curial-agencies |archivedate=2018-12-26 |language=en}}</ref>，並於6月9日宣布讓他繼續擔任聖職部的成員<ref>{{cite news |last1=Glatz |first1=Carol |title=Pope reconfirms clergy congregation members, appoints U.S.-born prelate |url=https://www.ncronline.org/news/vatican/pope-reconfirms-clergy-congregation-members-appoints-us-born-prelate |accessdate=2018-12-25 |agency=Catholic News Service |via=National Catholic Reporter |date=2014-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225172513/https://www.ncronline.org/news/vatican/pope-reconfirms-clergy-congregation-members-appoints-us-born-prelate |archivedate=2018-12-25 |language=en}}</ref>。此外，他現時亦是{{link-en|公教教育部|Congregation for Catholic Education}}、[[信理部|信理部]]、{{link-en|宗座文化理事會|Pontifical Council for Culture}}和{{link-en|宗座國際聖體大會委員會|Pontifical Committee for International Eucharistic Congresses}}的成員。<ref name="VaticanPO" />根據若望保祿二世1988年發出的《{{link-en|善牧 (宗座憲令)|Pastor Bonus|善牧}}》，國務院、{{link-en|聖部 (羅馬教廷)|Congregation (Roman Curia)|聖部}}和理事會成員的每一任期為5年。<ref>{{cite web |author1=John Paul II |title=PASTOR BONUS |url=http://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/en/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19880628_pastor-bonus.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2018-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226064945/http://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/en/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19880628_pastor-bonus.html |archivedate=2018-12-26 |language=en |date=1988-06-28}}</ref>

方濟各於2018年6月28日將韋萊升為主教級樞機，韋萊繼續以過橋聖母堂區作領銜之用，他不會因為沒有領[[羅馬城郊教區|羅馬城郊教區主教]]銜而跟其他主教級樞機有差別。<ref>{{cite web |title=RESCRIPTUM EX AUDIENTIA SS.MI: Rescriptum of the Holy Father Francis by which he has decided to co-opt into the Order of Bishops, equating them in all respects with the Cardinals holding the title of a suburbicarian Church, Cardinals Parolin, Sandri, Ouellet and Filoni, 26.06.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/06/26/180626c.html|publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-06-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190614174109/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/06/26/180626c.html |archivedate=2019-06-14 |language=en |date=2018-06-26}}</ref>

== 牧徽 ==
[[File:Coat_of_arms_of_Marc_Ouellet.svg|200px]]
牧徽盾牌上底色為天藍色，{{裏}}面有一個3個銀色山峰的山，山上有一個金色十字架。十字架和山的右邊和左邊分別有一個金色和一個銀色的的[[百合花飾|百合花飾]]。韋萊將盾牌的背景色定為天藍色是因為他希望牧徽可以代表他的出生地，百合花飾則代表魁北克，而山上的十字架是描述蒙特利尔的創始人在山上放置十字架的動作。牧徽上的格言「{{lang|la|Ut unum sint}}」意為「願眾人都合而為一」，出自《[[若望福音|若望福音]]》第十七章第21節。此外，[[教宗若望保祿二世|教宗若望保祿二世]]跟韋萊的格言有關。若望保祿二世發表的《{{link-en|願眾人都合而為一|Ut unum sint}}》跟這句格言一樣，這份通諭提及了韋萊曾經出任秘書長的[[宗座基督徒合一促進理事會|宗座基督徒合一促進理事會]]。<ref name="ECDQ" />

== 看法 ==

=== 神學 ===
《[[國家郵報|國家郵報]]》的報導中指韋萊一旦當選教宗的話將會「延續[[教宗本篤十六世|教宗本篤十六世]]的{{link-en|信理神學|Dogmatic theology}}思想」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Brean |first1=Joseph |title=Beyond the self-effacing facade, Canadian Cardinal Marc Ouellet is a cardboard cutout of Benedict XVI |url=https://nationalpost.com/news/canada/cardinal-marc-ouellet-is-cardboard-cutout-of-benedict-xvi |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=National Post |date=2013-02-15  |archivedate=2018-12-26 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>英國的《{{link-en|寫字板 (英國)|The Tablet|寫字板}}》亦指韋萊的神學思想與期刊《{{link-en|共融 (期刊)|Communio|共融}}》的創辦人若瑟·拉辛格（後來的本篤十六世）、[[漢斯·烏爾斯·馮·巴爾塔薩|漢斯·烏爾斯·馮·巴爾塔薩]]和{{link-en|亨利·德·呂巴克|Henri de Lubac}}所提倡的一致。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Lamb |first1=Christopher |title=Cardinal Ouellet refutes central Viganò claim |url=https://www.thetablet.co.uk/news/10831/cardinal-ouellet-refutes-central-vigan-claim |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=The Tablet |date=2018-10-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226083055/https://www.thetablet.co.uk/news/10831/cardinal-ouellet-refutes-central-vigan-claim |archivedate=2018-12-26 |location=United Kingdom |language=en}}</ref>

=== 《聖經》相對主義 ===
2011年2月，韋萊在[[馬德里|馬德里]]表示「教會內外因為《[[聖經|聖經]]》[[相對主義|相對主義]]而進入危機，這種主義主張拒認天主聖言的價值」。他亦指出「歐洲文化的根基正被動搖，並指有些人以[[國家利益|國家利益]]為由強行修改法律，從而試圖貶低[[基督宗教|基督宗教]]在歐洲起源的重要性」。此外，他提到「有[[世俗主義|世俗主義者]]主張將《聖經》相對化，令《聖經》變為{{link-en|多元宗教主義|Religious pluralism}}的一部分及成為『{{link-en|文化規範模型|Normative model of culture|文化規範}}的參考』而失去作用」。<ref>{{cite news |title=CARDINAL OUELLET WARNS AGAINST BIBLE CRISIS |url=http://www.zenit.org/e-31692 |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=Zenit News Agency |date=2011-02-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120926115213/http://www.zenit.org/e-31692 |archivedate=2012-09-26 |language=en}}</ref>

=== 就第二次梵蒂岡大公會議的解讀 ===
他認為很多天主教徒將[[梵蒂岡第二屆大公會議|梵蒂岡第二屆大公會議]]的訓導看得太開明，導致自己跟天主教的信仰脫節，韋萊表示相對主義令[[神職人員|神職人員]]減少、令曾接受正當宗教教育的人數下降及令[[左翼|左翼政治]]冒起，並認為舉行大公會議不是要得出這些結果。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Lewis |first1=Charles |title=Canadian cardinal to set tone for Church |url=https://nationalpost.com/holy-post/canadian-cardinal-to-set-tone-for-church |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=National Post |date=2010-08-19 |archivedate=2018-12-26 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 教會受到迫害 ===
[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]於2008年9月推出學生必讀的{{link-en|道德與宗教文化|Ethics and religious culture|道德與宗教文化課程}}，課程內容圍繞6至7種宗教。韋萊於一個月後譴責這個課程為「一個過激的入門課程」，並指「沒有歐洲國家曾嘗試過這樣做」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Soreau |first1=Marine |title=QUÉBEC : BOYCOTT DU COURS OBLIGATOIRE D'ÉTHIQUE ET DE CULTURE RELIGIEUSE |url=http://www.zenit.org/article-19949?l=french |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=Zenit News Agency |date=2009-01-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316160728/http://www.zenit.org/article-19949?l=french |archivedate=2012-03-16 |language=fr}}</ref>翌年，他表示[[天主教會|天主教會]]因為在[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]傳播天主教思想，而在該省正受到迫害。他認為「新生代的宗教教育並不足夠」，亦指魁北克省政府新批准的道德與宗教文化課程{{裏}}並沒有談及天主教信條。另外，他認為「除了省政府批准的課程外，亦應該設立一個專門談及《聖經》文化的課程，讓人們可以有選擇」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=White |first1=Hilary |title=Secular Quebec is Persecuting the Catholic Church: Quebec City Archbishop |url=https://catholicexchange.com/secular-quebec-is-persecuting-the-catholic-church-quebec-city-archbishop |accessdate=2018-12-24 |publisher=Catholic Exchange |date=2009-04-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224122105/https://catholicexchange.com/secular-quebec-is-persecuting-the-catholic-church-quebec-city-archbishop |archivedate=2018-12-24 |language=en}}</ref>

=== 公開道歉 ===
韋萊於2007年11月21日在魁北克的法語報章中刊登一封公開道歉信，他在信中為魁北克天主教會於1960年之前犯下的事情道歉，這些事情包括「[[天主教會性侵害案例|神父進行性侵犯行為]]」、「贊同[[反猶太主義|反猶太主義]]（和）[[種族主義|種族主義]]」、「歧視女性和[[同性戀者|同性戀者]]」及「漠視[[第一民族|第一民族]]」。<ref>{{cite news |title=Surprised by reactions, cardinal insists apology was an 'act of peace' |url=https://www.cbc.ca/canada/ottawa/story/2007/11/22/qc-cardinal1122.html |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=CBC News |date=2007-11-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071124034928/https://www.cbc.ca/canada/ottawa/story/2007/11/22/qc-cardinal1122.html |archivedate=2007-11-24 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Quebecers reluctantly accept archbishop's apology |url=http://www.cbc.ca/canada/montreal/story/2007/11/21/archbishop-quebec.html?ref=rss |accessdate=2018-12-26 |publisher=CBC News |date=2007-11-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071124214827/http://www.cbc.ca/canada/montreal/story/2007/11/21/archbishop-quebec.html?ref=rss |archivedate=2007-11-24 |language=en}}</ref>他在{{link-en|布沙爾-泰勒委員會|Bouchard-Taylor Commission}}上發言後選擇公開道歉以回應公眾；另外，他亦承認[[教宗若望保祿二世|教宗若望保祿二世]]一封於2000年3月發出、內容相似的信件激發他寫了這封公開道歉信。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Gyapong |first1=Deborah |title=Ouellet apology step in 'a journey of dialogue' |url=https://www.catholicregister.org/item/8401-ouellet-apology-step-in-a-journey-of-dialogue%E2%80%99 |accessdate=2018-12-27 |agency=Canadian Catholic News |via=The Catholic Register |date=2007-11-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181227032715/https://www.catholicregister.org/item/8401-ouellet-apology-step-in-a-journey-of-dialogue%E2%80%99 |archivedate=2018-12-27 |language=en}}</ref>

=== 墮胎 ===
韋萊於2010年5月在[[國會山莊_(加拿大)|加拿大國會山莊]]舉行的[[反墮胎|反墮胎]]集會上表示[[因姦成孕|因姦成孕者]]不能[[墮胎|墮胎]]。他認為「墮胎就好像謀殺一樣嚴重」，都是「道德罪行」，並指「即使因姦成孕的人都不能墮胎」。他所屬總教區的發言人之後表示韋萊的言論只是「純粹表達《[[天主教教理|天主教教理]]》的內容」。韋萊亦認同[[史蒂芬·哈珀|史蒂芬·哈珀]]政府不應該支持這些有意進行墮胎的國家，然而哈珀政府表示韋萊的言論與政府無關。<ref>{{cite news |title=Cardinal's abortion remarks anger politicians |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/cardinal-s-abortion-remarks-anger-politicians-1.890873 |accessdate=2018-12-27 |publisher=CBC News |date=2010-05-17 |archivedate=2018-12-27 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>同月26日，韋萊沒有改變有關「即使因姦成孕者都不能墮胎」的看法及指「如果他的言論令有意墮胎的女性受到傷害」，他感到抱歉。除此之外，他敦促[[加拿大政府|加拿大政府]]協助懷孕的女性保住胎兒並希望政府「可資助這些提供保留胎兒服務的診所」，令「這些診所與正受政府資助的墮胎診所都能得到平等對待」。他表示「如果加拿大政府不願意資助發展中國家為人進行墮胎和不願意協助這些已決定保住胎兒的女性，那麼政府的説法是自相矛盾」。另外，他認為「如果這樣做的話，加拿大在這個議題上會有很大進步」。<ref>{{cite news |title=Quebec archbishop defends comments on abortion |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/quebec-archbishop-defends-comments-on-abortion-1.516479 |accessdate=2018-12-27 |agency=The Canadian Press |via=CTV News |date=2010-05-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181227170140/https://www.ctvnews.ca/quebec-archbishop-defends-comments-on-abortion-1.516479 |archivedate=2018-12-27 |language=en}}</ref>

=== 同性戀 ===
韋萊在[[加拿大參議院|加拿大參議院]]作證期間促請參議員就[[加拿大同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]合法化議案投反對票，指同性婚姻是「[[假結婚|假結婚]]和虛構的」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Woods |first1=Allan |title=Marc Ouellet: Canadian pope prospect who says top job would be a 'nightmare' |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/feb/15/marc-ouellet-pope-prospect |accessdate=2018-12-28 |publisher=The Guardian |date=2013-02-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181228034548/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/feb/15/marc-ouellet-pope-prospect |archivedate=2018-12-28 |language=en}}</ref>此外，他認為同性婚姻是「一場[[人類學|人類學]]和道德危機」，並表示不知道同性婚姻「對人類有何價值」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Coren |first1=Michael |title=The men who could be pope: Cardinal Marc Ouellet |url=https://catholicherald.co.uk/news/2013/03/05/a-believer-who-thrives-in-a-secular-age/ |accessdate=2018-12-28 |publisher=Catholic Herald |date=2013-03-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181228034935/https://catholicherald.co.uk/news/2013/03/05/a-believer-who-thrives-in-a-secular-age/ |archivedate=2018-12-28 |language=en}}</ref>

=== 揀選主教 ===
作為{{link-en|主教部|Congregation for Bishops|主教部部長}}，他需要向教宗提議新主教的人選。韋萊在任期間，越來越多身為神學家和維護天主教信仰的神職人員獲任命為主教，這些主教包括[[安傑洛·斯科拉|安傑洛·斯科拉]]、[[類思·安多尼·塔格萊|類思·安多尼·塔格萊]]、{{link-en|嘉祿·J·查普特|Charles J. Chaput}}和{{link-en|嘉祿·莫雷羅德|Charles Morerod}}等等。他於2012年的時候認為「（天主教會）在世俗社會背景下的新主教要遵守教宗和教會的神學訓導、懂得如何處理行政工作及懂得傳播《[[福音書|福音書]]》」；另外，他指新主教「需要有能力闡述天主教信仰並在有需要的時候知道如何捍衛它」。韋萊亦警告「那些計劃以非正當途徑而升遷的神父和主教最好不要升遷」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Magister |first1=Sandro |title=Theologians, defenders of faith, prominent among recently named bishops worldwide |url=http://www.catholic-sf.org/news_select.php?newsid=2&id=59407 |accessdate=2018-12-28 |publisher=Catholic San Francisco |date=2012-01-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304084937/http://www.catholic-sf.org/news_select.php?newsid=2&id=59407 |archivedate=2012-03-04 |language=en}}</ref>

=== 兒童性虐待 ===
經過2018年的[[狄鐸·埃德加·麥卡里克|狄鐸·麥卡里克]]事件和於同年發表的{{link-en|大陪審團就賓夕凡尼亞州天主教會性虐待事件的調查|Grand jury investigation of Catholic Church sexual abuse in Pennsylvania|賓夕凡尼亞州天主教神父性虐待調查報告}}之後，韋萊於[[波茲南|波茲南]]回應記者提問的時候認為女性在教導神父們如何對付[[兒童性虐待|兒童性虐待]]問題上應該有更大角色並指教會需要更多女性參與教導。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Viatteau |first1=Michel |title=Cardinal says women should train priests to fight abuse 'crisis' |url=https://sg.news.yahoo.com/cardinal-says-women-train-priests-fight-abuse-crisis-050804444.html?guccounter=1 |accessdate=2018-12-28 |agency=AFP News |via=Yahoo |date=2018-09-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181228060545/https://sg.news.yahoo.com/cardinal-says-women-train-priests-fight-abuse-crisis-050804444.html?guccounter=1 |archivedate=2018-12-28 |language=en}}</ref>

=== 維加諾的指控 ===
{{link-en|嘉祿·瑪利亞·維加諾|Carlo Maria Viganò}}總主教指控[[教宗方濟各|教宗方濟各]]讓狄鐸·麥卡里克擔任天主教會內的職務，他認為方濟各不再適合出任教宗。此外，他同時提議韋萊要看清楚麥卡里克事件的來龍去脈。韋萊後來認為維加諾的指控並不正確。<ref>{{cite news |title=Cardinal Ouellet: Vigano in 'open and scandalous rebellion' against Pope Francis |url=https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/cardinal-ouellet-vigano-in-open-and-scandalous-rebellion-against-pope-francis-53755 |accessdate=2018-12-28 |publisher=Catholic News Agency |date=2018-10-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181228070507/https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/cardinal-ouellet-vigano-in-open-and-scandalous-rebellion-against-pope-francis-53755 |archivedate=2018-12-28 |language=en}}</ref>

